    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 92.</p><p>Heroic Perk: Mind Tricks</p><p>Prerequisite: Awakened Mind</p><p>You can cast the Suggestion spell at will without expending a spell slot. You cannot be affected by spells or magical effects that would sense your emotions or read your thoughts. When a creature attempts to read your thoughts or emotions, you can present false thoughts or feelings. The mind reader can notice their falseness by succeeding on a DC 30 Wisdom (Insight) check.</p></div>",
